high_descs: Turn right, go to counter with microwave.
Open microwave, remove egg to the right of the potato, close the microwave.
Turn right, proceed to counter.
Open right cabinet under counter, to the right of the lettuce.  Put egg in pan in cabinet.
Pick up pan with egg in it.  Close cabinet door.
Turn right to face far cabinet.
Put pan with egg in it on counter to left, past the sink.
anns.task_desc: Get egg from microwave, put in pan in cabinet, move to counter past sink.

Open the microwave take out the egg then close the microwave
Turn right then head to the cabinet beside the sink
Open the cabinet and put in the egg on the plate
Pick up the plate with egg and close the cabinet
Turn to your right facing the extended counter
Put the plate with egg on the edge of the counter beside the right side of the sink
anns.task_desc: Get the heated egg and put it on the counter

high_descs: walk to face the microwave oven
open the door, pick up the egg inside the microwave, close the door
walk right to face the counter to the left of the sink with lettuce
open the right cabinet door below the counter, put egg on the grey plate
pick up the grey plate from the cabinet, close the door

put the plate on the counter to the right of the sink
